            "text": "<h2>Bonus: 2025â€™s Golden Rule? Comfort = Confidence.</h2><p>Gone are the days when sarees meant being tied up tight. In 2025, itâ€™s all about <strong>easy, breezy confidence.</strong></p><ul><li>Drape your saree so you can <em>sit, dance, eat, and laugh</em> without fidgeting.<br/><br/></li><li>Choose lighter, flowy fabrics if you want carefree movementâ€”think organza, georgette, chiffon.<br/><br/></li><li>And donâ€™t hesitate to experiment: pre-stitched sarees, sarees with pants, or belted drapes are all super chic this year.</li></ul><h2>Sumana Speaks!</h2><p>Whatâ€™s one saree mistake youâ€™ve madeâ€”and how did you fix it? (We promise, weâ€™ve all tripped over our pleats at least once!) Drop your stories in the Instagram DM and tell us how your saree wins and woes.</p><p>Because truly, every saree story is a love story in progress.Â </p>",
